text:
Google has announced that it will phase out unlimited storage on Google Photos.

Any images users upload beyond June 1, 2021 will count towards the 15 GB limit imposed on Google accounts. After hitting that limit, users will have to pay for extra space. https://t.co/z8NBrKm59V
